{
  "stem": "5371.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they couldn't see us whether we're moving or not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we decided if they-- if we go and start to go into the forest, we start shooting, and we let a few people know to run.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it so happened they put us all into the barn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "About 5 o'clock in the morning, we heard a lot of noise.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we look out the barn, and there were five tanks with the thing pointing at the barn, the-- the--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The guns, yeah, pointing at the barn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I never seen Russians, and I never knew Russian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the women were there from the Lithuanian area, they-- they already experienced the Russian.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were under Russian rule already, so they knew the Russians.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they start screaming, Russians, Russians!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody's running out from the barn and the Russians sitting there on the tanks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The people who could converse with them spoke to them, and they were told to quickly move back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were a lot of horses and wagons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Germans who were running away from the Russians, they left their horses and wagons there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were told or we were told to grab whatever we can, any-- any horses and wagons and quickly move back, because they're only five tanks.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They can-- they can be pushed back by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Move back as far as we can into-- into town or whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we grabbed a wagon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "About-- yeah, before-- before I say that, as we're grabbing the wagons, I take a look and I see a familiar face.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, that German who shot that Jewish man was already in civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Russians, the-- the-- the SS that the Russians found, they shot them all.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
